FBIS3-36408 "drsov025_f_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Feb 1994 National Affairs Kravchuk Meets Crimean President Meshkov 4 Feb LD0402151594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1438 GMT 4 Feb 94 LD0402151594 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Efim Shvartsman] [Text] Kiev February 4 TASS -- Ukrainian President Leonid Kravchuk met on Friday the first popularly elected president of the Crimean semi-autonomous republic Yuriy Meshkov. Meshkov arrived in the Ukrainian capital after his inauguration ceremony in the Crimean administrative centre of Simferopol. Kravchuk congratulated Meshkov upon his inauguration and noted that the two have a lot of common problems to discuss. The Ukrainian president said they should meet more than once in the future, adding that he would like to get first-hand information about Crimea's problems from the president of the republic.
